T4	p 423 726	The European Union's Life for Citrus campaign, which includes Spain, Portugal, France and Italy, is developing strategies to stop the spread of huanglongbing (HLB). Caused by the bacterium Candidatus liberibacter, this disease is spread by insects and can completely destroy a citrus tree in five years.
